{{nihongo|'''Tadahiro Ando'''|安藤 忠恕|Andō Tadahiro|extra=March 9, 1941 – April 30, 2010}} was the [[governor of Japan|Governor]] of [[Miyazaki Prefecture]] from 2003 to 2006. In 2009, Ando was convicted of bribe-taking and [[Bid rigging|bid-rigging]] which were offences that he had committed earlier when he was governor.<ref>[http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nn20090328a4.html Bribed, bid-rigging governor is sent up]</ref><ref>[http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nn20100501b1.html Ex-Miyazaki Gov. Ando dies at 69]</ref>
